rules.failed_sql_sample: SELECT a.ADMISSION_YEAR, ROUND(100 * SUM(CASE WHEN surgery_count >= 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*), 2) AS reoperation_rate_pct FROM ( SELECT a.HADM_ID, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.ADMITTIME) AS ADMISSION_YEAR, COUNT(DISTINCT p.ORDERID) AS surgery_count FROM ADMISSIONS a JOIN PROCEDUREEVENTS p ON a.HADM_ID = p.HADM_ID WHERE a.ADMISSION_TYPE = 'SURGICAL SAME DAY ADMISSION' GROUP BY a.HADM_ID, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM a.ADMITTIME) ) surgery_counts GROUP BY a.ADMISSION_YEAR
